    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Got it, so it's an adjunct there. Does the depth of the tree change significantly between those two interpretations? Like, does the VP-attachment version result in a much \"busier\" or more complex branching structure compared to the NP attachment? I'm trying to get a feel for how the tree density changes when you add more constituents to the VP.",
